{"article_id":"fUegm4hCVQlcfZuR","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"As Democratic House Minority Leader Nancy Pelosi , D-Calif. , faces a tricky climb","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"to build the support from her own party for her retake the gavel in January ,","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"she ' s getting an unlikely source of support :","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"Republicans .","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"Pelosi has repeatedly said","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"that she is confident","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"she has the votes","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"to become speaker","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"-- a position","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"she held between 2007 and 2011 , the last time","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"Democrats held the majority in the House .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"But she is facing a brewing revolt from her own members ,","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"with a number of Democrats signing a letter","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"pledging not to support her .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"Fox News confirmed Thursday","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"that at least 17 House Democrats ,","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"including incumbents and incoming members ,","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"have signed on to a document","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"they will not support Pelosi on the House floor for speaker .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"A Democrat familiar with the effort says","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"they are trying to add more names","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"before the letter is publicly released .","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"If all those Democrats vote against Pelosi on the floor ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"Pelosi would not have the votes for speaker .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"To get the gavel ,","depth":4},{"id":26,"text":"Pelosi will first need to pick up a majority of the Democratic caucus in internal leadership elections ,","depth":5},{"id":27,"text":"then go on to win an absolute majority of the House .","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"'NEVER NANCY ' REVOLT BREWING AGAINST PELOSI ,","depth":4},{"id":29,"text":"AS REBELLIOUS HOUSE DEMS REFUSE SUPPORT FOR SPEAKER BID","depth":4},{"id":30,"text":"But","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"as she faces an increasingly tight race ,","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"a number of Republicans are floating the idea","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"of offering her support in the House","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"-- thinking","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"that it would help them in the long term .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"President Trump tweeted after the midterms","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"that","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"if she struggled ,","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"\" perhaps we will add some Republican votes \"","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"although it was not clear","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"if this remark was serious or tongue-in-cheek .","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"On Thursday , Republican Tom Reed said","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"that","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"if Pelosi embraced a bipartisan package of rules reforms","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"that would make it easier for members to get legislation to the floor ,","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"he could envision supporting her .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"\" A Democratic candidate","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"who embraces these rules reforms ,","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"I will stand with , \"","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"he told CNN .","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"\" I am so frustrated with this institution being a top-down driven organization ...","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"it is time","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"to change this","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"and","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"if Nancy Pelosi is the only one","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"that ' s there ,","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"I ' m open to it . \"","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"Reed did concede","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"that there would be \" significant backlash \" from other Republicans .","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"But other Republicans have also suggested","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"backing her bid","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"-- as it could help them in the long term .","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"`` She reminds the American people","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"why they do n't like politics .","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"She reminds them why they do n't like Democrats , quite frankly , ''","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"Republican strategist Chris Wilson said Friday on \" Fox and Friends. \" `` The best thing in the world for Republicans is to have her in that role . ''","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"Citing Trump ' s remarks last week ,","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"Wilson suggested","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"that Republicans should back the California Democrat .","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"`` Republicans are not going to have a speaker of the House .","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"So why not try and ... put her back in that chair ? ''","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"he asked .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"Pelosi , at a press conference Thursday , she dismissed the idea","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"that she would need Republican help","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"to win the gavel .","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"`` I intend to win the speakership with Democratic votes , ''","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"she later said ,","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"adding","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"that she had `` overwhelming support '' in her caucus .","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"In 2016 , Pelosi fended off a leadership challenge from Rep. Tim Ryan , D-Ohio .","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"During a recent appearance on Fox News ' \" Cavuto , \" Ryan said ,","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"\" I don ' t think","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"this is a done deal yet \"","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"in terms of Pelosi becoming speaker again .","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"Ryan also says","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"he \" hopes","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"somebody does \" challenge Pelosi .","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"On Friday , Pelosi met for 45 minutes with Rep. Marcia Fudge , D-Ohio ,","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"who is mulling a prospective leadership challenge .","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"Other Democrats have been more supportive .","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"House Progressive Caucus Chairwoman Pramila Jayapal , D-Wash. , told Fox News Friday","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"that \" she has the experience . \"","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"\" She ' s someone","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"who get things done .","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"We don ' t need someone with a learning curve , \"","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"she said ,","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"adding","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"that \" we need to deliver some real wins pretty quickly . \"","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":197,"left":126,"right":196,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":102,"right":125,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":102,"left":100,"right":101,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":100,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":125,"left":122,"right":124,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":108,"right":121,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":108,"left":4,"right":107,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":107,"left":5,"right":106,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":106,"left":103,"right":105,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":8,"right":104,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":110,"right":120,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":11,"right":109,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left"